pageProduct.name: Thompsons Mood Support 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Mood Support supports healthy mood balance and reduce and relieve symptoms of mild anxiety.

Thompson's Mood Support is formulated with a blend of herbs and nutrients to:
- Support healthy mood balance.
- Reduce & relieve symptoms of mild anxiety.
- Support general health & wellbeing.
- Assist wits synthesis of neurotransmitters.

Size: 60 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Support healthy mood balance.
• Reduce & relieve symptoms of mild anxiety.
• Support general health & wellbeing.
• Assist wits synthesis of neurotransmitters.

Warnings

St John's Wort affects the way many prescription medicines work, including the oral contraceptive pill. Consult your doctor. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.
Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Active ingredient per tablet:
Hypericum perforatum (St. John's Wort) ext. 409mg.
derived from dry herb top flowering 2.5g.
std. to contain Hypericins 1.35mg.
Crocus sativus (Saffron) ext. 15.75mg.
derived from dry stigma 52.5mg.
Levomefolate calcium 216.6mcg.
equiv. Levomefolic acid 200mcg.
Mecobalamin (Co-Methylcobalamin) 75mcg.
Pyridoxal-5-phosphate monohydrate 31.4mg.
equiv. Pyridoxine (Vitamin B6) 20mg.
Tyrosine 250mg.
Zinc citrate dihydrate 37.4mg.
equiv. Zinc 12mg.

Contains: Soya bean

Allergen Contains: Soybean

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours| Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Nuts| Sesame Seeds

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
